, idealistische und phänomenologische Perspektiven auf zeitgemäße Konzeptionen ästhetischer Wissensformen.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 20. Sep 2019) 0aAesthetics. 4aDeutscher Idealismus. 4aErkenntnis. 4aGerman idealism, knowledge, art. 4aKunst. 70(DE-601)1044510760(DE-588)4135841-7aSinnlichkeit2gnd 70(DE-601)1060990860(DE-588)4070914-0aErkenntnistheorie2gnd 70(DE-601)1062007550(DE-588)4045660-2aPhänomenologie2gnd 70(DE-601)1063509270(DE-588)4011784-4aDeutscher Idealismus2gnd 70(DE-601)1063823650(DE-588)4005248-5aBegriff2gnd 70(DE-601)1064005410(DE-588)4000626-8aÄsthetik2gnd 7aPHILOSOPHY / Aesthetics.2bisacsh1 aAsmuth, Christoph, eeditor.1 aRemmers, Peter, eeditor.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2015z9783110439687oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Philosophy 2015z9783110438680oZDB-23-DPH0 cEPUBz97831103839040 cprintz978311034620640uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783110346244423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783110346244.jpg  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA14ALL  aPDA16SSH  aPDA1ALL  aPDA2  aPDA2HUM  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2015  aZDB-23-DPHb2015